10:05.672 --> 10:07.307 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You saw that glass ceiling
break.

10:07.340 --> 10:09.108 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

10:09.142 --> 10:13.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NANCY PELOSI: 1984, I was chair
of the host
committee at the San Francisco
convention.

10:13.746 --> 10:21.254 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I can tell you -- I can just
drum it up
immediately -- the thunderous
response that

10:21.287 --> 10:24.023 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
