is called the
Red to Blue Committee.

20:38.270 --> 20:43.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have 38 people who are on
that list of
seats where we think we have an
opportunity

20:44.009 --> 20:45.177 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to pick those up for Democrats.

20:45.211 --> 20:47.713 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
