20:47.746 --> 20:50.416 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are still challenges when
we're looking
at women running for office.

20:50.449 --> 20:54.220 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think how we're going to
correct that
is what's going on right here.

20:54.253 --> 20:57.857 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When we get a woman in the White
House, I
think that it is going to be
easier to get

20:57.890 --> 21:00.593 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
