21:00.626 --> 21:02.928 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I hope that we make some
tremendous gains
over the years.

21:02.962 --> 21:04.897 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KAMALA HARRIS, California
