21:49.175 --> 21:51.076 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
before.

21:51.110 --> 21:55.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that's an important point to
make to everybody,
not just girls, not just women,
not just people

21:55.514 --> 21:57.216 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
