22:19.738 --> 22:21.340 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Is it a matter of confidence?

22:21.373 --> 22:22.341 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Is it money?

22:22.374 --> 22:23.342 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What is holding women back?

22:23.375 --> 22:25.144 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

22:25.177 --> 22:27.813 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHERI BUSTOS: It is very, very
different when
we're recruiting a woman vs.
recruiting a

22:27.846 --> 22:29.148 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
