because we all
have different life experiences.

26:32.024 --> 26:36.962 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when decisions are being
made that are
going to impact so many people,
it's important

26:36.995 --> 26:43.202 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that we have considered all the
ramifications
based on how it will roll out.

26:43.235 --> 26:47.506 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The more diverse the group of
people are who
are making the decision, the
better the decision

26:47.539 --> 26:51.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
will be, especially when you're
talking about
the decisions that are being
made by the president

